Titolo: The Walking Dead: Saints & Sinners

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: The Walking Dead: Saints & Sinners is a virtual reality first-person shooter survival horror game for Windows, PlayStation 4, Oculus Quest, and Oculus Quest 2, developed by Skydance Interactive. It is based on the Skybound Entertainment comic book series The Walking Dead by Robert Kirkman. Initially released on Steam and Oculus platform on January 23, 2020, it was also released on PlayStation VR in May 2020. It was then released on Oculus Quest in October 2020 under the "tourist edition" surname.